result.text: A grand "thousand-person dance" recently took place in Sanjiang, Liuzhou. Duoye (多耶) is a collective song and dance of the #Dong ethnic group, combined with labor, without musical accompaniment. The Dong people are an ethnic group that live together. In early society, activities such as hunting and sacrificial rituals required collective cooperation to complete. If you are interested in experiencing a unique #song and #dance performance, you definitely shouldn't miss it.
